serviceTag: "federal"
title: "FERS Retirement Planning | Capital Wealth"
description: "Maximize your FERS retirement benefits. Expert guidance on annuity calculations, eligibility, MRA, high-3 salary, and FERS supplement. Capital Wealth helps federal employees retire with confidence."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
