      <h2 class="fed-ed-fers-section-title">When Can You <em>Retire</em>?</h2>
      
      <p class="fed-ed-fers-body">FERS offers multiple retirement pathways, each with different requirements and benefit calculations. Understanding your options is crucial for optimizing your retirement date and maximizing lifetime benefits.</p>
      
