    <section id="calculation" class="fed-ed-fers-section">
      <span class="fed-ed-chapter-label">CHAPTER III: CALCULATION</span>
      <h2 class="fed-ed-fers-section-title">The <em>Formula</em> Behind Your Pension</h2>
      
      <p class="fed-ed-fers-body">Your FERS annuity calculation follows a specific formula, but the details matter significantly. Small changes in timing, service credit, or salary can impact your lifetime benefits by thousands.</p>
      
      <div class="fed-ed-glass-card">
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-serif-display); color: #003870; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">FERS Annuity Formula</h3>
        <div style="text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-serif-display); font-size: 1.5rem; color: #003870; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <strong>Years of Service × High-3 Salary × Multiplier</strong>
        </div>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <h4 style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: #F09F54; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Standard Multiplier</h4>
            <p style="font-family: var(--font-serif-display); font-size: 2rem; color: #003870; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">1.0%</p>
            <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b;">Most employees</p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <h4 style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: #F09F54; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Enhanced Multiplier</h4>
            <p style="font-family: var(--font-serif-display); font-size: 2rem; color: #003870; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">1.1%</p>
            <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b;">Age 62+ with 20+ years</p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <h4 style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: #F09F54; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Special Category</h4>
            <p style="font-family: var(--font-serif-display); font-size: 2rem; color: #003870; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">1.7%</p>
            <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b;">LEO/ATC/Fire (first 20 yrs)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="fed-ed-fers-body">Your high-3 average salary is calculated using your highest average basic pay during any 3 consecutive years of federal service. This includes locality pay but excludes overtime, bonuses, and other premium payments.</p>
      
      <p class="fed-ed-fers-body">From Mike's book: "Tom Merrick learned the hard way that his final promotion pushed him into a higher tax bracket without significantly increasing his high-3 — the timing cost him thousands in net retirement income."</p>
